1) Cloudwatch - Global. To moniter Events, CPU utilization, Logs, Alarms.

2) S3- Serverless.To store static files (with/without encryption)

3) EC2 - To track status of instance of server deployed. For manual scaling if required.

4) Lambda(FaaS Function as a service) - 
Serverless. Specific to region. 
Develope will deploy lambda function and don't have to manage server for it. Thus serverless for developer. 
A virtual functions which is limited by time(max 15 min), run on demand, automatic scaling
